**Additional Protections**:
- **Rate limiting**: Prevents rapid-fire attack attempts (10 transfers/minute per user)
- **Optimistic locking**: Version column detects concurrent modifications even if locks fail
- **Comprehensive audit logging**: All attempts (successful and failed) logged with request correlation IDs
- **Graceful degradation**: Returns 503 with retry guidance when system is under contention
- **Lock TTL**: Prevents indefinite lock holding if process crashes (10 second TTL)
- **Account status validation**: Prevents transfers involving frozen/inactive accounts
- **Error categorization**: Different error codes allow clients to implement appropriate retry logic
